title: Katie Culp on A League of Their Own
itunes:title: Katie Culp on A League of Their Own
description:
Chuck met Katie Culp when she came through for him to replicate his beloved Last Chance Garage patch for his lost baseball cap. A few years later, she comes in to talk about her movie crush, the baseball classic, A League of Their Own.
